issue.title: Create Image request daemon
issue.body: Every night, request new images and cache

issue.title: Create Settings Activity
issue.body:
Settings activity will have the following functions:

- Check artists to display (checkboxes)
- Set overscan (Button to new activity with movable border) (editable text fields for manual input)
- Set time between change of backdrop (time chooser)
- Set adaptive matting based on avg color (on/off)
 - Display artist name and date (on off toggle)

issue.title: Create main layout
issue.body:
Matting should be 3 inches on each side (measure in pt)
Overscan should be added to matting (in dip)
ImageView to display image
